{"name":"Sword +1, Flaming","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"range":{"short":0,"medium":0,"long":0},"save":"","pattern":"transparent","description":"<p>Melee: Close quarters weapon (5′ or less).</p>\n<p>Bursts into flames, on command. When flaming:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Casts light:</strong> In 30′ radius.</li>\n<li><strong>Can set things alight:</strong> Treated as a torch, for purposes of setting things on fire (e.g. a <em>web</em> spell).</li>\n<li><strong>Inflicts fire damage:</strong> Which may have special effects on certain creatures.</li>\n<li><strong>Grants an attack bonus:</strong> Against certain types of creature:\n<ul>\n<li>+2 vs trolls (or other creatures that cannot regenerate fire damage).</li>\n<li>+2 vs pegasi, hippogriffs, and rocs (or other bird-like creatures).</li>\n<li>+3 vs treants (or other plant-based creatures).</li>\n<li>+3 vs undead.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> The sword blazes until commanded to cease.</li>\n</ul>","damage":"1d8+1","bonus":1,"tags":[{"title":"Melee","value":"Melee"}],"slow":false,"missile":false,"melee":true,"cost":0,"equipped":false,"weight":60,"counter":{"value":0,"max":0}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-crossguard-flanged-red.webp","effects":[],"_id":"GC2BjKefJuekjbPs"}
