{"name":"Sword +1, Energy Drain","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"range":{"short":0,"medium":0,"long":0},"save":"","pattern":"transparent","description":"<p>Melee: Close quarters weapon (5′ or less).</p>\n<p>Drains the life energy of its victims.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>On a successful hit:</strong> The wielder may command the sword to drain the victim&rsquo;s life energy.</li>\n<li><strong>Energy drain:</strong> In addition to suffering normal damage, the target permanently loses one experience level (or Hit Die). This incurs a loss of one Hit Die of hit points, as well as all other benefits due to the drained level (e.g. spells, saving throws, etc.). A character&rsquo;s XP is reduced to the lowest amount for the new level. A person drained of all levels dies.</li>\n<li><strong>Charges:</strong> The sword may drain a total of 1d4+4 levels. Once this many levels have been drained, it becomes a normal magical sword +1.</li>\n</ul>","damage":"1d8+1","bonus":1,"tags":[{"title":"Melee","value":"Melee"}],"slow":false,"missile":false,"melee":true,"cost":0,"equipped":false,"weight":60,"counter":{"value":0,"max":0}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-crossguard-flanged-red.webp","effects":[],"_id":"kQRVcj2OW6E8baCh"}
